title: Final Draft Advice & Salary Cap League Strategy
description:
Field Yates, Mike Clay and Daniel Dopp break down the latest news around the league before talking salary cap league strategy to come away with the best players at the best values. Then, the crew dives into the final advice you need to be ready for your fantasy drafts.
